# Indented block value preservation

```scalascript
val input = "  host"
println(runLayout(PSameIndent(3), input, input, Position(0), IndentContext.at(3)))
println(Parser.regex("[a-z]+").block.withIndent(3).parseLayoutWith(input, IndentContext.at(1)))
```
